    <Paragraph>A Menu is a control that allows hierarchal organization of elements associated with commands or event handlers. Each <Run FontWeight="Bold">Menu</Run>
 can contain multiple MenuItem controls. Each <Run FontWeight="Bold">MenuItem</Run>
 can invoke a command or invoke a Click handler. A <Run FontWeight="Bold">MenuItem</Run>
 can also have multiple <Run FontWeight="Bold">MenuItem</Run>
 elements as children, forming a submenu.
